<item>
            <title>[LU-17457] LNet ip2nets and routes parameters do not work with large NIDs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17457</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The lnet ip2nets and routes kernel parameters do not support large NIDs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[ 8930.431892] LNetError: 10f-e: Error parsing &apos;ip2nets=&quot;tcp1(eth4) 2601:8c1:c180:2000::cbdd&quot;&apos;
[ 8930.437576] LNetError: 110-0: here...............................|-----------------------|
[ 8930.442493] LNetError: 119-9: Error -22 parsing ip2nets
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[ 8733.796368] LNetError: 10f-e: Error parsing &apos;routes=&quot;tcp2 2601:8c1:c180:2000::cbde@tcp1&quot;&apos;
[ 8733.801309] LNetError: 110-0: here.............................|-----------------------|
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
